&lt;p&gt;Hello, I’m Pepper, a Data Analytics Engineer on the Data Team at Karrot.Our team&amp;rsquo;s vision is to &amp;quot;make user-focused decisions through data every day.&amp;quot; So we don&amp;rsquo;t just focus on reliably collecting massive amounts of data — we also work on transforming it into trustworthy, easy-to-use formats.In this post, I&amp;rsquo;d like to share how we moved away from manually calculating Activation analysis with ad hoc queries and elevated it to a shared data layer used across the organization.BackgroundThe&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>